# Rubio

A clean, lightweight Python wrapper for the Rubika Bot API.

## Installation

```bash
pip install Rubio
```

## Usage

```python
from rubio import Bot

bot = Bot("YOUR_TOKEN")
bot.send_message("CHAT_ID", "Hello from Rubio!")
```
